The paper discusses the behavior of two combinational rules for temporal attribute data fusion for target type estimation, which is a problem commonly addressed in the fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), control systems (cs.SY), computer vision (cs.CV), cryptography (cs.CR), and machine learning (cs.LG).
